OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,FA former town mayor has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor three years for assisting her son
OL,8,Fafter he had filmed himself raping an
OL,9,Funconscious 15-year-old girl who he
OL,10,Fhad given drug-laced vodka.
OL,12,FNaheed Ejaz, 61, who served as mayor
OL,13,Fof Bracknell Forest from May 2023 to
OL,14,FMay 2024, was found guilty at
OL,15,FWinchester Crown Court of a charge of
OL,16,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
