PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,FShe was convicted of stalling police
OL,7,Fas they sought to arrest her son Diwan
OL,8,FKhan, of Bracknell, Berkshire,
OL,9,Ffollowing the rape of the girl in his
OL,10,Fcar in the Fleet and Farnborough area
OL,11,Fof Hampshire in July 2024.
OL,13,FThe 41-year-old, who served as his
OL,14,Fmother's mayoral consort, was jailed
OL,15,Ffor 12 years and given a five-year
OL,16,Fextended licence period upon release
OL,17,Ffor rape and perverting the course of
OL,18,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,FKhan was also made subject to a sexual
OL,7,Fharm prevention order for 20 years, an
OL,8,Findefinite restraining order, and will
OL,9,Fbe on the sex offenders register for
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FA Hampshire Constabulary spokesman
OL,13,Fsaid: "Khan had supplied the girl with
OL,14,Fvodka laced with MDMA, and then raped
OL,15,Fher while she was unconscious and
OL,16,Ffilmed himself doing so, the court
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,19,F"The incident was reported to police
OL,20,Fvia a third party on September 10 that
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,26,@uD@GOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,F"When officers attended Khan's home
OL,7,Faddress on September 12, his mother
OL,8,FNaheed Ejaz, 61, came to the front
OL,9,Fdoor but did not open it for two
OL,10,Fminutes, the jury was told.
OL,12,F"When officers did enter the address
OL,13,Fto arrest Khan, their body-worn
OL,14,Ffootage captured a conversation
OL,15,Fbetween the two in Urdu, in which they
OL,16,Ftalked about hiding something.
OL,18,F"The conversation was later translated
OL,19,Fand Ejaz was arrested. Despite
OL,20,Fmultiple searches, the phone has not
OL,21,Fbeen found."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
