PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,FA Bracknell Forest Council spokesman
OL,7,Fconfirmed that Khan had acted as
OL,8,Fmayoral consort but had conducted no
OL,9,Fcivic functions or engagements in 2024.
OL,11,FA portrait of Ejaz, a Labour
OL,12,Fcouncillor, had been removed from a
OL,13,Fgallery of former mayors at the
OL,14,Fcouncil's Time Square office, the
OL,15,Fspokesman added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
