OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,FSusan Halliwell, the council's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,8,Fwith the brave young girl whose life
OL,9,Fhas been undoubtedly changed forever
OL,10,Fdue to the heinous crimes of former
OL,11,Fmayor Naheed Ejaz and former mayoral
OL,12,Fconsort Diwan Khan.
OL,14,F"While the crimes were committed in
OL,15,FEjaz and Khan's personal life outside
OL,16,Fof their civic roles, it does not make
OL,17,Fthem any less abhorrent.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,F"To further reassure and safeguard our
OL,7,Fresidents, we have started a thorough
OL,8,Finvestigation into the taxi licensing
OL,9,Fof both Ejaz and Khan."
OL,11,FThey held separate and distinct
OL,12,Flicences which were issued and revoked
OL,13,Fat different times."
OL,15,FDetective Constable Lee Clement said:
OL,16,F"The victim in this case has shown
OL,17,Fconsiderable bravery during the
OL,18,Finvestigation, and in having to relive
OL,19,Fher experience in court.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WOUuD@TO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777629986
OL,3,CFormer mayor jailed for aiding rapist
OL,4,Cson
OL,6,F"This attack continues to have a
OL,7,Fsignificant impact on her mental
OL,8,Fhealth.
OL,10,F"We hope that this result helps in
OL,11,Fsome way in her recovery.
OL,13,F"Khan targeted a vulnerable teenage
OL,14,Fgirl, and then, along with his mother
OL,15,FEjaz, tried to cover up evidence to
OL,16,Fhinder our investigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
